                    dated to 1743,
                    concerning mostly the construction of the church of <placeName ref="LOC6533DabraSahayQwe"/>. The letter is attested in 
                    <ref type="mss" corresp="BLorient481"/> and <ref type="mss" corresp="BLDaethb3"/>.
